		<RichText x="66" y="666" width="505" height="212" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">影响<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>提供热量的系数，不影响无附着火攻击提供的热量。<br/>熔岩辉龙像的热效率为95%。<br/>热量条的积攒=</span><span color="#ffdfbf">热效率×元素量×25</span><span>。<br/>「岩之人」状态下受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，会根据此次攻击的元素量n，在当n&gt;0或n=0时积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">6.786n%</span><span>(23.75n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2%</span><span>(7)热量；「熔焰之龙」状态时则积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2.969n%</span><span>(23.75n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.875%</span><span>(7)热量。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>热效率变为45%；当元素量n&gt;0时，「岩之人」状态下积攒的热量降为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3.214n%</span><span>(11.25n)热量；「熔焰之龙」状态则为积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1.406n%</span><span>(11.25n)热量。<br/>多人模式下的热效率亦存在衰减：1/2/3/4人，热效率为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">95%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">76%</span><span>/<br/></span><span color="#ffdfbf">67.857%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">63.33%</span><span>。</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>热效率为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">45%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">36%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">32.1%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">30%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
