		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-熔岩辉龙像%B7炽烈流焰.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1396" y="267" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-熔岩辉龙像%B7炽烈流焰.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1520" y="233">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="443" height="303" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">辉龙具有2种状态：「岩之人」和「熔焰之龙」；两个状态可互相转化，且受到<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>伤害均会累积热量，且热效率相对于正常难度有所下降；<br/>「岩之人」状态下</span><span color="#ffdfbf">350</span><span>点；「熔焰之龙」状态下</span><span color="#ffdfbf">800</span><span>点，且初始拥有</span><span color="#ffdfbf">12.5%</span><span>(100)的热量，自身常驻</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>。<br/>「岩之人」状态下积攒热量，攒满后进入「熔焰之龙」状态；<br/>「熔焰之龙」状态下攒满热量后辉龙像将直接瘫痪13s，此状态下一旦受</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>或</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>攻击时，会立即失去</span><span color="#ffdfbf">18.75%</span><span>(150)热量。<br/>「熔焰之龙」状态下累积热量达50%和100%时，均会损失当前</span><span color="#ffbfbf">15%</span><span>生命值；瘫痪结束后，或热量不足会退回「岩之人」状态。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfff">(N6) </span><span>存在</span><span color="#ff9999">最大扣血伤害</span><span>1500000点；</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-熔岩辉龙像%B7炽烈流焰.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1376" y="246" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
